<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="664" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[113,1089,220,820]" pageId="3" pageNumber="664">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[113,243,763,787]" pageId="3" pageNumber="664">Comments.</emphasis>
All 
<specimenCount box="[290,434,764,788]" pageId="3" pageNumber="664" type="generic">12 specimens</specimenCount>
of 
<taxonomicName authority="Löbl, 2009" authorityName="Löbl" authorityYear="2009" box="[471,591,765,788]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Akarbatrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="664" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis box="[471,591,765,788]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="664">Akarbatrus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[598,696,764,788]" pageId="3" pageNumber="664" rank="genus">gen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
collected are males. This is possibly due to differences in phenology (females may appear later than males).
</paragraph>
